name: Sure Baby Mañana Tote
description:
"Sure Baby, Mañana." Jack Kerouac's "On The Road" Quote Floral Graphic Tote Bag, because, it was always mañana - a lovely word and one that probably means heaven.

100 % Cotton, handprinted and measures 16"x15" (excluding handle), with handle length measuring 9". A sturdy tote, perfect for carrying all your essentials on your cross-country adventures.

Tote should be hand-washed in cold to lukewarm water, and can be ironed on the reverse or by placing a piece of cotton fabric on the print.
